body.description: Looking for eye-catching accent pieces that will add character to your indoor space? When you think of home decor, what usually comes to mind are wall art, mirrors, candles, or figurines. While such pieces add style to your home, your living space might still need a final finishing touch to tie everything together. Decorating your home with books is one way to give any room a sophisticated makeover. If you're looking for unique faux books to spruce up your living room, bedroom, or an empty bookshelf, our linen-covered tomes are the perfect choice. Breathe new life into any bare space with the Dabster Guys Linen-Covered Decor Books. Showing off gorgeous linen fabric covers, our decorative books have what it takes to steal the show in your home. Each book measures 8.5x5.7x0.9", so you'll have no trouble displaying them on your nightstand, work desk, mantel, coffee table, or bookshelf. Aside from beautifying your space, these decorative books also set an encouraging tone in your home. The book covers feature inspirational words and phrases, such as "Inspire," "Dream," "Believe," "Inspire Others," "Think Positive," and "Be Grateful." Each set includes 3 books, all of which have blank pages that you can write on. Also included in the package are a 34.6" wooden bead garland, 100" of hemp rope, and a Thank You card — all packed in an elegant, gift-worthy box. Need more time to decide? Here are more reasons to love our fabric-covered book decorations: - Measures 8.5x5.8x3" when stacked - Foil-stamped design on the covers - Available in two sets: three light covers/two dark and one light cover - Suitable for decorating modern or rustic homes and offices Watch your indoor space come to life in an instant. Add the Dabster Guys Linen-Covered Decor Books to your cart NOW!

reviews.reviewText: What a beautiful touch. Beautifully well made note books. Gorgeous binding linen material, very elegant and good weight to them. It comes with twine and beads.. I used the beads to decor another piece. Came very well packaged, and protected very well. Excellent purchase, I am so happy and I totally recommend.

reviews.reviewText: Books came shrink wrapped in plastic, I opened them and placed them on my office cabinet. After five days they have warped and will no longer lay flat.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 29, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I can’t wait to get my floating shelves up around my TV to display these beautiful decor books and beads. They are very pretty and sturdy. You’d never know they were not real books. But then again, with the blank pages, they could be used as journals. So they have a dual function.

reviews.reviewText: The books are so beautiful! I loved the packaging, all the books came wrapped in plastic ensuring that they arrive in perfect condition. They look great on my side table and the best part is that I can write my own journal on them.
